<h2 id="make-meaningful-labels">Make meaningful labels</h2>

<p>Unfortunately often in use, links and buttons with labels like: click here and learn more. <strong>For the user such labels are meaningless</strong> and only <strong>understandable in combination with further content.</strong></p>

